                                it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney \
                                College in Virginia, looked up one.'
                                },
                                {
                                    title: 'Assistant Manager, C# ESRI GIS Application Developer',
                                    sub: 'Telekom Malaysia Berhad',
                                    grade: 'Grade: CGPA: 3.71 (First Class Honours)',
                                    time: '(month 2019 - month 2019)',
                                    text: 'Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. \
                                It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making \
                                it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney \
                                College in Virginia, looked up one.'
                                },
                                {
                                    title: 'Assistant Manager, C# ESRI GIS Application Developer',
                                    sub: 'Telekom Malaysia Berhad',
                                    time: '(month 2019 - month 2019)',
                                    text: 'Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. \
                                It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making \
                                it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney \
                                College in Virginia, looked up one.'
